S|# CEO Dashboard Feature Migration — YVON 2.0 → YVON-OS|> What stays, what moves, what dies.
S|The Old CEO Dashboard|YVON 2.0 had a 2-tab CEO Command Dashboard: // - **Briefing tab** — Strategic briefing, priorities, dec queue, intelligence feed // - **Operations tab** — System strip (graph view, token usage, workload, ses sync), project graph, agt kanban // Legacy code also had: // - **Overview** — KPI gauges (ROAS/CAC/Brand Health), key numbers (removed) // - **Situation** — agt kanban, intelligence feed // - **Act** — dec queue, priorities, decisions live // - **Done** — Activity log, source reports // - **
S|Where Each Feature Goes|### LIVE DATA → Dashboard/Home (new morning overview) // \| Feature \| Current \| Destination \| Why \| // \|---------\|---------\|-------------\|-----\| // \| **Token Usage** \| CEO > Operations \| **Dashboard/Home** \| Real data (DeepSeek balance, $17.76, per-agt spend). This is a genuine morning metric. \| // \| **System Health** \| CEO > Operations \| **Dashboard/Home** \| "System healthy / X agents live" — quick status before CEO dives in \| // \| **agt Kanban** \| CEO > Situation \| **Agen
S|What Remains as "Dashboard/Home" (the morning landing)|The YVON-OS `/dashboard` page becomes the **7-second scan** before the CEO dives into dec Queue: // ``` // ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ // │  DASHBOARD                                 8:42 AM IST │ // │  ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐  │ // │  │ DEEPSEEK │ │ AGENTS   │ │ QUEUE    │ │ SYSTEM   │  │ // │  │ $ 17.76  │ │ 13 live  │ │ 7 items  │ │ Healthy  │  │ // │  │ balance  │ │ running  │ │ waiting  │ │ all clear│  │ // │  └──────────┘ └───────
